{"word":"G657 - ἀποτάσσομαι - apotássomai - ap-ot-as'-som-ahee - Bid farewell","slug":"G657","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποτάσσομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>apotássomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ap-ot-as'-som-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bid farewell"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B1;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03C4;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03C3;&#x03C3;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - apotassomai</b> - <i>ap-ot-as'-som-ahee</i><p/>Middle voice from <a href=\"#/G575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>; literally to <i>say adieu</i> (by departing or dismissing); figuratively to <i>renounce:</i> - bid farewell, forsake, take leave, send away."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1296\">G1296</a>, <a href=\"#/G1297\">G1297</a>, <a href=\"#/G1299\">G1299</a>, <a href=\"#/G2004\">G2004</a>, <a href=\"#/G392\">G392</a>, <a href=\"#/G4367\">G4367</a>, <a href=\"#/G5001\">G5001</a>, <a href=\"#/G5021\">G5021</a>, <a href=\"#/G506\">G506</a>, <a href=\"#/G5292\">G5292</a>, <a href=\"#/G5293\">G5293</a>, <a href=\"#/G812\">G812</a>, <a href=\"#/G813\">G813</a>, <a href=\"#/G814\">G814</a>"}]}